Business Brief -- Ball Corp.:
   Venture Planned to Invest
   In Can Factories in China
Since 1987, Ball been a minority owner in a plant in the
city of Guangzhou, which makes a variety of metal and plastic
containers.
   Ball, based in Muncie, Ind., will hold an undisclosed
minority stake in the venture; Futec, the majority partner,
is a newly formed entity owned by a group of Hong Kong
companies.